":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11578,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/bakhil-refuse-bless-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":14615,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Misers refuse to bless the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe miser is one in whose presence I am mentioned, but he does not send blessings upon me.\" Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3546 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/11\/tashahhud-sitting-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":14615,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say when sitting in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: While praying behind the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, we were saying, \u201cPeace be upon Allah, peace be upon this person.\u201d The Prophet told us one day, \"Verily, Allah Himself is Peace. When one of you sits in prayer, let him say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/29\/tashahhud-fi-hajjah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14615,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Testifying to faith in prayer and in need","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught us to bear witness to faith in prayer and to bear witness to faith in times of need. Bearing witness in prayer is to say, \u201cGreetings are for Allah, as are prayers and pure things.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8141,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/preferred-tashahhud-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":14615,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Variants of Prayer&#8217;s ending supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would teach us the testimony of faith in prayer, just as he would teach us a chapter from the Quran. The Prophet would say, \u201cGreetings, blessings, prayers, and good words are for Allah. Peace be upon you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u062